Nuestro problema: Extranjeros que llegan a un país hispanohablante y no entienden o tienen dificultades con el idioma

Brainstorming:
Application installed - It will be this
Community of speakers to help people who need with notifications
Support service for several languages
Pre-installed sentences and words

Names:
Habla Español

System requirements:
-Needs to cover at least basic situations
-Easy to use
-Quick access
-Open source
-Tiene que ser grátis
-Needs to allow to add languages, words and sentences
-Easy to update
-Quick processing of requests
-Lightweight
-Must not use much battery / not be CPU-intensive
-Must allow feedback / rating / Did it help you?
